1. In Part I, headings 3A002.g.2, 6A001.a.1.b.2, 6A001.a.1.b.3, 6A001.a.1.b.4, 6A001.a.1.b.5, 6A001.a.2.d, 8A002.o.3.a, 8A002.p and 8D002 shall be deleted.
2. Part II shall be amended as follows:
(a) headings 1C012.a, 3A201.a, 3A228.c, 6A203.b and 6E201 shall be deleted;
(b) heading 1E001 shall be replaced by the following: ">TABLE>";
